#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.31"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.31:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 4. Devatāvagga → sekhaparihāniyavaggo (bj)
msgctxt "an6.31:0.2"
msgid "4. Devatāvagga"
msgstr "4. Deities"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.31:0.3"
msgid "31. Sekhasutta"
msgstr "31. A Trainee"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli3.330"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.31:1.1"
msgid "“Chayime, bhikkhave, dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr "“These six things lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

msgctxt "an6.31:1.2"
msgid "Katame cha?"
msgstr "What six?"

msgctxt "an6.31:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kammārāmatā, bhassārāmatā, niddārāmatā, saṅgaṇikārāmatā, indriyesu "
"aguttadvāratā, bhojane amattaññutā—"
msgstr ""
"They relish work, talk, sleep, and company. They don’t guard the sense "
"doors, and they eat too much."

msgctxt "an6.31:1.4"
msgid ""
"ime kho, bhikkhave, cha dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr "These six things lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.31:2.1"
msgid "Chayime, bhikkhave, dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr "These six things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

msgctxt "an6.31:2.2"
msgid "Katame cha?"
msgstr "What six?"

msgctxt "an6.31:2.3"
msgid ""
"Na kammārāmatā, na bhassārāmatā, na niddārāmatā, na saṅgaṇikārāmatā, "
"indriyesu guttadvāratā, bhojane mattaññutā—"
msgstr ""
"They don’t relish work, talk, sleep, and company. They guard the sense "
"doors, and they don’t eat too much."

msgctxt "an6.31:2.4"
msgid ""
"ime kho, bhikkhave, cha dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr "These six things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.31:2.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
